#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:595
msgid "CacheBlend"
msgstr "CacheBlend"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:597
msgid ""
"CacheBlend reuses cached KV at shifted (non-prefix) positions by "
"recomputing a small subset of tokens.  The operator manages it as a "
"second CRD, ``CacheBlendEngine``, plus a **mutating admission webhook** "
"that injects the pure-Python ``lmcache-cacheblend`` vLLM plugin into your"
" serving pods -- so you do **not** rebuild the vLLM image.  See "
":doc:`/kv_cache_optimizations/blending` for the technique itself."
msgstr "CacheBlend 通过重计算一小部分令牌来重用在偏移（非前缀）位置的缓存 KV。该操作符将其管理为第二个 CRD ``CacheBlendEngine``，以及一个 **变更入站 webhook**，该 webhook 将纯 Python 的 ``lmcache-cacheblend`` vLLM 插件注入到您的服务 Pod 中，因此您 **不** 需要重建 vLLM 镜像。有关该技术的详细信息，请参见 :doc:`/kv_cache_optimizations/blending`。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:604
msgid "It has two halves the operator runs together:"
msgstr "它有两个部分，操作符一起运行："

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:606
msgid ""
"a GPU-resident ``blend_v3`` engine (``lmcache server --engine-type "
"blend``), deployed as a DaemonSet with the **same GPU model as** "
"``LMCacheEngine`` (``privileged`` + ``runtimeClassName: nvidia`` + "
"``NVIDIA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=all`` + ``hostIPC``, and **no** "
"``nvidia.com/gpu`` claim) so it shares the vLLM GPU for same-device CUDA "
"IPC; and"
msgstr "一个驻留在 GPU 上的 ``blend_v3`` 引擎 (``lmcache server --engine-type blend``)，作为 DaemonSet 部署，**与** ``LMCacheEngine`` **相同的 GPU 型号** (``privileged`` + ``runtimeClassName: nvidia`` + ``NVIDIA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=all`` + ``hostIPC``，并且**没有** ``nvidia.com/gpu`` 声明)，因此它共享同设备的 vLLM GPU 进行 CUDA IPC；并且"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:611
msgid "the vLLM-side plugin, injected into opted-in pods by the webhook."
msgstr "vLLM 侧插件，通过 webhook 注入到选择加入的 pod 中。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:614
msgid "Additional Prerequisites"
msgstr "附加先决条件"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:616
msgid "Beyond the operator prerequisites above:"
msgstr "超出上述操作符的先决条件："

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:618
msgid ""
"**cert-manager** -- the webhook's serving certificate is issued by a "
"cert-manager ``Issuer`` + ``Certificate``.  Install it before ``make "
"deploy``:"
msgstr "**cert-manager** -- webhook 的服务证书由 cert-manager ``Issuer`` + ``Certificate`` 颁发。在 ``make deploy`` 之前安装它："

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:626
msgid ""
"**Deploy with the webhook** -- use ``make deploy`` (not ``make run``, "
"which is controller-only and disables the webhook via "
"``ENABLE_WEBHOOKS=false``)."
msgstr "**使用 Webhook 部署** -- 使用 ``make deploy``（而不是 ``make run``，后者仅为控制器并通过 ``ENABLE_WEBHOOKS=false`` 禁用 Webhook）。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:628
msgid ""
"**Pod Security Standards** -- the webhook injects "
"``hostIPC``/``privileged``, which the ``baseline``/``restricted`` "
"profiles reject, so label the engine's and the vLLM pod's namespaces "
"``pod-security.kubernetes.io/enforce=privileged``."
msgstr "**Pod 安全标准** -- webhook 注入 ``hostIPC``/``privileged``，而 ``baseline``/``restricted`` 配置文件会拒绝这些，因此将引擎和 vLLM pod 的命名空间标记为 ``pod-security.kubernetes.io/enforce=privileged``。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:633
msgid "Deploying a CacheBlendEngine"
msgstr "部署 CacheBlendEngine"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:656
msgid ""
"The engine runs ``lmcache server --engine-type blend`` as a DaemonSet and"
" emits a ``my-cacheblend-connection`` ConfigMap with the "
"``CBKVConnector`` ``kv-transfer-config`` (the operator wires the node-"
"local Service host/port and the ``cb.*`` tunables)."
msgstr "该引擎以 DaemonSet 方式运行 ``lmcache server --engine-type blend``，并生成一个包含 ``CBKVConnector`` ``kv-transfer-config`` 的 ``my-cacheblend-connection`` ConfigMap（操作符将节点本地服务的主机/端口和 ``cb.*`` 可调参数连接起来）。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:662
msgid "Opting a vLLM Pod In"
msgstr "选择 vLLM Pod 参与"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:664
msgid ""
"Label the pod template for the webhook and bind it to an engine by name."
"  Launch vLLM via the image **ENTRYPOINT** (args only) -- a ``command: "
"[\"/bin/sh\", \"-c\", ...]`` wrapper is skipped, since appended args "
"would not reach ``vllm serve``:"
msgstr "为 webhook 标记 pod 模板，并按名称将其绑定到引擎。通过镜像 **ENTRYPOINT** 启动 vLLM（仅参数）——跳过 ``command: [\\\"/bin/sh\\\", \\\"-c\\\", ...]`` 包装器，因为附加的参数将无法到达 ``vllm serve``："

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:697
msgid ""
"The webhook injects the plugin init container, ``PYTHONPATH``, "
"``hostIPC``, the private-image pull secret, and the required CacheBlend "
"vLLM flags (``--attention-backend CUSTOM``, ``--kv-transfer-config`` from"
" the engine's connection ConfigMap, ``--block-size 64``, ``--pipeline-"
"parallel-size 1``, ``--no-enable-chunked-prefill``, ``--no-async-"
"scheduling``, ``--enforce-eager``). You supply only the model and your "
"non-CacheBlend flags."
msgstr "Webhook 注入插件初始化容器、``PYTHONPATH``、``hostIPC``、私有镜像拉取密钥，以及所需的 CacheBlend vLLM 标志（``--attention-backend CUSTOM``、``--kv-transfer-config`` 来自引擎的连接 ConfigMap、``--block-size 64``、``--pipeline-parallel-size 1``、``--no-enable-chunked-prefill``、``--no-async-scheduling``、``--enforce-eager``）。您只需提供模型和非 CacheBlend 标志。"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:705
msgid "Verifying Injection"
msgstr "验证注入"

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:707
msgid "The webhook mutates **Pods**, not the Deployment, so inspect a pod:"
msgstr "该 webhook 变更的是 **Pods**，而不是 Deployment，因此请检查一个 pod："

#: ../../source/mp/operator.rst:714
msgid ""
"If nothing was injected, check the pod's ``lmcache.ai/cacheblend-skip-"
"reason`` annotation: ``command-override`` (a ``sh -c`` wrapper was used),"
" ``kv-transfer-config-present`` (you set your own), ``engine-not-found`` "
"(the ``<name>-connection`` ConfigMap is missing), ``payload-image-unset``"
" (the engine's ``injection.payloadImage`` has no repository), or "
"``target-container-not-found`` (the requested ``targetContainer`` / "
"``cacheblend-container`` annotation names a container the pod does not "
"have). With ``failurePolicy: Ignore`` a webhook/cert problem also leaves "
"the pod un-mutated silently -- confirm the operator pod is ``Running`` "
"and the ``MutatingWebhookConfiguration`` exists."
msgstr "如果没有注入任何内容，请检查 pod 的 ``lmcache.ai/cacheblend-skip-reason`` 注解：``command-override``（使用了 ``sh -c`` 包装器）、``kv-transfer-config-present``（您设置了自己的）、``engine-not-found``（缺少 ``<name>-connection`` ConfigMap）、``payload-image-unset``（引擎的 ``injection.payloadImage`` 没有仓库），或 ``target-container-not-found``（请求的 ``targetContainer`` / ``cacheblend-container`` 注解指定了 pod 中不存在的容器）。在 ``failurePolicy: Ignore`` 的情况下，webhook/cert 问题也会使 pod 静默保持未变更 -- 确认操作员 pod 正在 ``Running`` 状态，并且 ``MutatingWebhookConfiguration`` 存在。"

